title: Knitting by Nature 19 Patterns for Scarves, Wraps, and More by S
description:
In this follow-up to her wildly popular books Ocean Breezes and Nature's Wrapture, Sheryl Thies has outdone herself with a stunning new collection of nature-inspired designs. Revel in knitting ideas gathered from a wide array of flowers, grasses, and vines. 
Choose from exquisite designs, including scarves, shawls, wraps, and shrugs 
Capture the beauty of plant forms with lace, cables, bobbles, and other knitting stitches 
Enjoy modern designs that require minimal or no finishing
